#. Translators: Summary/title for this add-on
#. to be shown on installation and add-on information found in add-on store.
#: buildVars.py:15
msgid "UnigramPlus"
msgstr "UnigramPlus"

#: buildVars.py:19
msgid "This add-on adds a lot of hotkeys for quick navigation through the main elements of the Unigram application, convenient interaction with Chat messages, and also adds many small improvements that make working in Unigram much easier"
msgstr "此插件新增了许多快捷键，可快速浏览 Unigram 应用的主要元素、方便地与聊天消息交互，并加入许多小改进，使使用 Unigram 更加轻松。"

#: buildVars.py:26
msgid ""
"- Fixed unwanted chat folder unread-count announcements and limited file transfer progress announcements to Unigram file uploads and downloads.\n"
"- Added a setting to open the UnigramPlus sounds folder so users can replace bundled sound files.\n"
"- Added an up-arrow action that moves from the message edit field to the last focused message.\n"
"- Added separate Traditional Chinese and Simplified Chinese localizations."
msgstr ""
"- 修复聊天文件夹未读数量变化被不必要读出的问题，并将文件传输进度读出限制为 Unigram 的文件上传和下载。\n"
"- 新增打开 UnigramPlus 声音文件夹的设置，用户可替换内置声音文件。\n"
"- 新增上方向键操作，可从消息编辑字段移到最后获得焦点的消息。\n"
"- 新增独立的繁体中文和简体中文本地化。"


